metadata.name: Saul G - #hashtag (feat. Metth)
metadata.description: Continuing his Turkish G funk works without slowing down, Saul G meets music lovers with his entertaining works #hashtag, accompanied by Metth, one of the essential names of RedKeys Music. The duo brings life to the NFT characters of Flufworld Party Bear. Emphasizing living in the moment and having fun, the song also draws attention with its effective sound embellished with west coast motifs. The mixing and mastering processes of the work, produced by Charaf Beatz, bear the signature of Barry Allen (Khontkar). Artwork of the song carries the signature of Wipe3D. The strong collaboration of Saul G and Metth #hashtag was released on all digital music platforms as of May 19, 2023.
